Change Log
==========

v0.1.1
------
- Defined snap-camera-network as a python 3 script so that it can be run
  without explicitly invoking the Python 3 interpreter first.
- Added egg timer.

v0.1.0
------
- Can specify mode at start up (`snap-camera.py --mode network`).
- Fixed timimg (no longer used `while now() < pic_time: pass`).

v0.0.2
------
- Added fbi into dependencies.
- Fixed viewer bug: camera would crash if there were no images present

v0.0.1
------
- Fixed network mode bug: camera would crash if no ethernet cable was present.
- Fixed overlay folder bugs: camera would crash if no overlays directory,
  camera would not detect overlays.

v0.0.0
------
- Initial dev release.
